merged.mergedContent:
# https://github.com/vkouk/joyspot-api/blob/05b27a36b91c17031cd891837960a70ba805c596/app/graphql/gql/schema.graphql:
# import * from 'user.graphql'

type Query {
  me: User!
  users: [User!]!
}

type Mutation {
  signup(
    email: String!
    password: String!
    name: String!
    avatar: String
  ): User!
  signin(email: String!, password: String!): User!
  signout: Boolean!
  updateUser(email: String, name: String, avatar: String): User!
}

# https://github.com/vkouk/joyspot-api/blob/05b27a36b91c17031cd891837960a70ba805c596/app/graphql/gql/user.graphql:
type User {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  email: String!
  password: String!
  avatar: String
}
